  80:1:1:"The first word of verse (80:1) is a perfect verb (<span class=\"at\">فعل ماض</span>). The verb is third person masculine singular. The verb's triliteral root is <i class=\"ab\">ʿayn bā sīn</i> (<span class=\"at\">ع ب س</span>)."
